column5: It seems that noone fishes or replys to question about Rainey. We were there in June and did real well. Am going back Thursday and am wondering if and where the walleye might be. We stay just off Black Point behing Commissioners Bay. Is there any thing biting on Seine Bay or Swell Bay.Thank you for any and all help.If you ever need any info on fishing pools 7 or 8 on the Mississippi, email me at [email protected] last gentleman we helped prefish won the tourney and $4000, he did thank us.
Thank you very much for the help with the new site, again, thank you. fsttlkr

Thanks for the link, alot of great help. I'm headed up there next Thursday and if anyone's out there early next week, let me know how you did. It's supposed to get a little colder and I would like to know how the fish have reactted.
